questions.text:
Quyidagi mahsulotlar narxlarining yig‘indisini hisoblang va total o‘zgaruvchiga yozing.
```javascript
const products = [{p: 120}, {p: 80}, {p: 50}];
let total = 0;
// kerakli kodni to'ldiring
// total nihoyatida 250 bo'lishi kerak
```

options.A:
```javascript
for (let i in products) {
  total += i.p;
}
```

options.B:
```javascript
for (const item of products) {
  total += item.p;
}
```

options.D:
```javascript
const sum = products.map(x => x.p);
total += sum;
```

questions.text:
Kod nomlar uzunligi 3 dan katta bo‘lganlarini katta harflarga o‘tkazishi kerak, ammo xato bor. Xatoni to‘g‘rilab to‘g‘ri natija chiqadigan variantni tanlang.
```javascript
const names = ["Ali","Olim","Laylo","Zo"];
const out = names.map(n => n.length > 3);
for (const n of out) {
  n = n.toUpperCase();
}
```

options.C:
```javascript
let out = [];
for (let i in names) {
  if (names[i].length > 3) out.push(names[i].toUpperCase());
}
```

options.D:
```javascript
const out = names.map(n => n.toUpperCase()).filter(n => n.length > 3 === true);
```

